{"article_id":"YnmM0j1ulu0BKK5v","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"On Twitter the rapper claims","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"he 's being `` used","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"to spread messages","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"I do n't believe in . ''","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"He has been a vocal supporter of President Trump","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"but this decision appears to centre around a campaign","depth":11},{"id":6,"text":"he was linked to","depth":11},{"id":7,"text":"known as Blexit .","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"Run by Conservative commentator Candace Owens","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"it encourages black Americans to quit the Democratic party .","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"She claimed","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"the musician had designed clothing for the campaign ,","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"something which the rapper has now denied .","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"Skip Twitter post by @ kanyewest","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"I introduced Candace to the person","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"who made the logo","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"and they didn ' t want their name on it","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"so she used mine .","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"I never wanted any association with Blexit .","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"I have nothing to do with it .","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"- ye","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"( @ kanyewest )","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"October 30 , 2018 Report","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"The rapper tweeted :","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"`` My eyes are now wide open .","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"I am distancing myself from politics","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"and completely focusing on being creative . ''","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"It seems Kanye West intends to step away from politics altogether now .","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"Skip Twitter post 2 by @ kanyewest","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"My eyes are now wide open","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"and now realize","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"I ' ve been used","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"to spread messages","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"I don ' t believe in .","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"I am distancing myself from politics","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"and completely focusing on being creative ! ! !","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"- ye","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"( @ kanyewest )","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"October 30 , 2018 Report","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"Writing to his 28.7 million followers","depth":5},{"id":40,"text":"the musician said :","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"`` I support creating jobs and opportunities for people","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"who need them the most .","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"`` I support prison reform ,","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"I support common-sense gun laws","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"that will make our world safer .","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"`` I support those","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"who risk their lives","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"to serve and protect us","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"and I support holding people","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"who misuse their power","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"accountable . ''","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"It 's not the first time ,","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"the rapper ,","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"who wants to be referred to as Ye ,","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"has had to clear up his political beliefs .","depth":4},{"id":56,"text":"Earlier this year he came under fire for for saying","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"that the 13th amendment of the US Constitution ,","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"which brought an end to slavery ,","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"should be abolished","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"- a statement","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"that he later clarified .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"Apparently he meant to write `` amend '' .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"And his performance on the American comedy show Saturday Night Live a few weeks ago sparked outrage and amusement in equal measure .","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"The 41-year-old ,","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"who is married to Kim Kardashian ,","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"wore a hat with Donald Trump 's slogan `` Make America Great Again ''","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"and apparently gave an unscripted , off-air rant in support of the president .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"Excerpts","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"filmed by the audience","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"and shared on social media","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"show the rapper discussing his support for President Trump , his pledge","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"to run for president in 2020","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"and the need for a `` dialogue not a diatribe '' .","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"`` So many times I talk to a white person","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"and [ they ] say ,","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"'How could you like Trump ,","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"he 's racist ? ' ''","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"`` Well ,","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"if I was concerned about racism","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"I would 've moved out of America a long time ago . ''","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"Kanye West has been very upfront about his support for President Trump .","depth":5},{"id":83,"text":"The pair have met several times","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"discussing issues","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"including employment and criminal justice reform .","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"However stars","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"including Snoop Dogg , T.I . and John Legend","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"have criticised Kanye West","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"for meeting the US leader .","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"Kanye West ended this latest series of messages","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"saying :","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"`` I believe in love and compassion for people","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"seeking asylum","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"and parents","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"who are fighting","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"to protect their 